<content>1 XWiki Application Testing with Selenium

Available tests can be found on the [test suite&gt;Selenium.AllTests] page.

#set($doc = $xwiki.getDocument('Selenium.Selenium'))
#set($testsuiteurl = $escapetool.url("$xwiki.getURL('Selenium.AllTests', 'view', 'xpage=plain')"))
#set($queryString = "TestRunner.html?test=$testsuiteurl&amp;resultsUrl=../postResults")
#set($url = $xwiki.getPlugin('zipexplorer').getFileLink($doc, 'selenium.zip', $queryString))

Click &lt;a href="$url"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; to execute these tests in the Selenium Test Runner.
